@startuml
title LeninKart Jira -> GitOps -> ArgoCD Deployment Flow

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Segoe UI
skinparam ArrowColor #334155
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.3
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam sequenceParticipant {
  BackgroundColor white
  BorderColor #475569
}

actor Operator
participant "Jira" as Jira
participant "GitHub Actions\nDeploy From Jira" as GHA
participant "Self-hosted Runner" as Runner
participant "deployment-poc\norchestrator" as POC
participant "leninkart-infra\n(dev)" as Infra
participant "ArgoCD" as Argo
participant "Kubernetes\nk3d-leninkart-dev" as K8s
participant "project-validation" as PV

Operator -> Jira : create / maintain deployment ticket
Operator -> GHA : workflow_dispatch(jira_ticket)
GHA -> Runner : schedule job on self-hosted runner
Runner -> POC : execute orchestrator
POC -> Jira : fetch issue + parse metadata
POC -> Jira : progress comment\nworkflow_triggered / jira_validated
POC -> POC : validate metadata\nresolve target\nacquire lock
POC -> Jira : progress comment\ntarget_resolved / lock_acquired
POC -> Infra : update values-dev.yaml\ncommit + push
POC -> Jira : progress comment\ngitops_commit_pushed
Infra -> Argo : new Git revision available
POC -> Argo : wait for sync + health\nexact revision check
POC -> Jira : progress comment\nargocd_sync_started
Argo -> K8s : reconcile application
Argo --> POC : Synced + Healthy\nexact revision
POC -> Jira : progress comment\nargocd_synced_healthy / post_checks_completed
POC -> Jira : final comment + transition
POC --> GHA : deployment-result artifact
PV -> GHA : validate workflow run UI
PV -> Infra : validate Git commit UI
PV -> Argo : validate app UI
PV -> K8s : validate live app reachability

note right of GHA
Current trigger model is manual.
Jira ticket creation alone does not
auto-dispatch the workflow yet.
end note

@enduml
